  "text": "Taken together, the reasons for the discrepancy between the results from Povedano JM/Degryse AL and those from Liu et al. remain unclear and are difficult to interpret. Based on the outcome of TERT mutations in FIP we and others hypothesize that these families developed lung fibrosis because of progressive telomere shortening in the alveolar epithelium [CITATION_1] 131] .",
